cvxTreeSetSelectionMode
form [in] form name
field [in] field number
mode [in] tree view control selection mode 

 0: No selection; 

 1: Single selection; 

 2: Multiple selection; 

 3: Extended selection; 

 4: Contiguous selection

This function sets the selection mode of a tree widget.

